,” after debuting in fifth place with previews last week, opened on April 3 and climbed […]"}, "summary_zh": "根据 Artisan Gateway 的数据，环球影业出品的《超级马里奥银河大电影》在 4 月 3。", "published_at": "2026-04-06T07:04:35+00:00", "source_media": "Variety"}, {"id": 264, "link": "https://variety.com/2026/tv/reviews/star-wars-maul-shadow-lord-review-clone-wars-1236706487/", "title": "《星球大战：摩尔 — 暗影领主》是《克隆人战争》传奇的一个参差不齐但充满希望的延伸：电视评论", "images": [], "metadata": {"summary_en": "Next month, the “Star Wars” franchise will return to theaters after an astonishing seven-year absence with Jon Favreau’s “The Mandalorian and Grogu,” a feature spinoff of the director’s hit Disney+ series “The Mandalorian.” The premiere is a confirmation of what was already clear to fans: that since 2019 — the year both “The Mandalorian” and “The […]"}, "summary_zh": "下个月，《星球大战》系列电影将在阔别七年之后重返影院，由乔恩·费儒执导的《曼达洛人和格罗古》，该片。", "published_at": "2026-04-06T07:01:00+00:00", "source_media": "Variety"}, {"id": 316, "link": "https://variety.com/2026/tv/reviews/star-wars-maul-shadow-lord-review-clone-wars-1236706487/", "title": "《星球大战：摩尔 — 暗影领主》是《克隆人战争》传奇的一个参差不齐但充满希望的延伸：电视评论", "images": [], "metadata": {"summary_en": "Next month, the “Star Wars” franchise will return to theaters after an astonishing seven-year absence with Jon Favreau’s “The Mandalorian and Grogu,” a feature spinoff of the director’s hit Disney+ series “The Mandalorian.” The premiere is a confirmation of what was already clear to fans: that since 2019 — the year both “The Mandalorian” and “The […]"}, "summary_zh": "下个月，《星球大战》系列电影将在阔别七年之后重返影院，由乔恩·费儒执导的《曼达洛人和格罗古》，该片。", "published_at": "2026-04-06T07:01:00+00:00", "source_media": "Variety"}, {"id": 317, "link": "https://variety.com/2026/film/reviews/faces-of-death-review-1236706326/", "title": "《死亡面孔》评论：一部 70 年代风格的 B 级恐怖电影迎合了人们对“真实”恐怖片日益增长的胃口", "images": [], "metadata": {"summary_en": "The idea that a sicko like Arthur isn’t just a serial killer — he’s part of the new anything-goes attention economy! — is a provocative bu