riticism for Polymarket for allowing users to bet on the date the U.S. would confirm the rescue of Air Force service members shot down over Iran."}, "summary_zh": "一名民主党国会议员严厉批评 Polymarket 允许用户押注美国确认营救在伊朗上空被击落的空军军人的日期。", "published_at": "2026-04-05T19:36:03+00:00", "source_media": "TechCrunch"}, {"id": 376, "link": "https://techcrunch.com/2026/04/05/copilot-is-for-entertainment-purposes-only-according-to-microsofts-terms-of-service/", "title": "根据微软的使用条款，Copilot“仅用于娱乐目的”", "images": ["https://techcrunch.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/GettyImages-2041281128-e1712563728365.jpg?resize=1200,676"], "metadata": {"summary_en": "AI skeptics aren’t the only ones warning users not to unthinkingly trust models’ outputs — that’s what the AI companies say themselves in their terms of service."}, "summary_zh": "人工智能怀疑论者并不是唯一警告用户不要不假思索地相信模型输出的人——人工智能公司在服务条款中也是这么说的。", "published_at": "2026-04-05T18:51:37+00:00", "source_media": "TechCrunch"}]}, "体育娱乐": {"main": {"id": 335, "link": "https://variety.com/2026/film/box-office/ranveer-singh-dhurandhar-the-revenge-174-million-globally-1236709179/", "title": "兰维尔·辛格执导的《杜兰达尔：复仇》全球票房突破 1.74 亿美元，成为第一部北美票房突破 2500 万美元的印度电影", "images": ["https://variety.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Dhurandhar-The-Revenge.jpg?crop=0px%2C25px%2C1000px%2C562px&resize=1000%2C563", "https://sb.scorecardresearch.com/p?c1=2&c2=6035310&c4=&cv=3.9&cj=1", "https://variety.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Dhurandhar-The-Revenge.jpg?w=1000&h=667&crop=1"], "metadata": {"summary_en": "Jio Studios and B62 Studios’ “Dhurandhar: The Revenge” has crossed INR1,622 crores ($174.4 million) worldwide through its third weekend, becoming the first Indian film to surpass $25 million in North America and €1 million ($1.1 million) in Germany. The Aditya Dhar-directed spy-action sequel’s India gross stands at $132.1 million. In Germany, the film established itself […]"}, "summary_zh": "Jio Studios 和 B62 Studios 的《杜兰达尔：复仇》截至第三周末，全球票房已突破 162.2 亿印度卢比（1.744 亿美元），成为第一部在北美票房超过 2500 万美元、在德国票房超过 