t facile idea. Yet that’s part of what gives \"Faces of Death\" the texture of a ''70s grindhouse movie. They often had ideas too. \"Faces of Death\" is \"ambitious\" trash, with the courage of its own gaudy thematic grandiloquence."}, "summary_zh": "像亚瑟这样的疯子不仅仅是一个连环杀手，他还是新的随心所欲的注意力经济的一部分！ ——这是一个具有挑。", "published_at": "2026-04-06T03:30:11+00:00", "source_media": "Variety"}, {"id": 191, "link": "https://variety.com/2026/film/reviews/faces-of-death-review-1236706326/", "title": "《死亡面孔》评论：一部 70 年代风格的 B 级恐怖电影迎合了人们对“真实”恐怖片日益增长的胃口", "images": [], "metadata": {"summary_en": "The idea that a sicko like Arthur isn’t just a serial killer — he’s part of the new anything-goes attention economy! — is a provocative but facile idea. Yet that’s part of what gives \"Faces of Death\" the texture of a ''70s grindhouse movie. They often had ideas too. \"Faces of Death\" is \"ambitious\" trash, with the courage of its own gaudy thematic grandiloquence."}, "summary_zh": "像亚瑟这样的疯子不仅仅是一个连环杀手，他还是新的随心所欲的注意力经济的一部分！ ——这是一个具有挑。", "published_at": "2026-04-06T03:30:11+00:00", "source_media": "Variety"}], "secondary": [{"id": 225, "link": "https://variety.com/2026/film/box-office/ranveer-singh-dhurandhar-the-revenge-174-million-globally-1236709179/", "title": "兰维尔·辛格执导的《杜兰达尔：复仇》全球票房突破 1.74 亿美元，成为第一部北美票房突破 2500 万美元的印度电影", "images": ["https://variety.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Dhurandhar-The-Revenge.jpg?crop=0px%2C25px%2C1000px%2C562px&resize=1000%2C563"], "metadata": {"summary_en": "Jio Studios and B62 Studios’ “Dhurandhar: The Revenge” has crossed INR1,622 crores ($174.4 million) worldwide through its third weekend, becoming the first Indian film to surpass $25 million in North America and €1 million ($1.1 million) in Germany. The Aditya Dhar-directed spy-action sequel’s India gross stands at $132.1 million. In Germany, the film established itself […]"}, "summary_zh": "Jio Studios 和 B62 Studios 的《杜兰达尔：复仇》截至第三周末，全球票房已突破 162.2 亿印度卢比（1.744 亿美元），成为第一部在北美票房超过 2500 万美元、在德国。", "published_at": "2026-0